metadata.name: Streetscape Stories
metadata.description: Captured from the upper deck of a double-decker bus in London, this photograph encapsulates a dynamic urban scene. The view encompasses a busy road with the words “bus stop” etched into the asphalt, while an intense and dramatic sky looms above. In the foreground, two individuals patiently await the arrival of the bus. The bustling thoroughfare is adorned with a blend of restored historic buildings and contemporary stores, offering a striking visual contrast that reflects the evolving nature of the cityscape.
